bilingual.source: She is a renowned intellectual and writer.
bilingual.target: 她是一位著名的知识分子和作家。

bilingual.source: An intellectual plays an important role in society.
bilingual.target: 知识分子在社会中扮演着重要的角色。
她是位年轻的知识分子。
我们以为他是个知识分子。
他是一个有教养的知识分子。

bilingual.source: I was born in an intellectual family.
bilingual.target: 我出生在一个知识分子家庭。
知识分子（可能是单调枯燥的人）。

bilingual.source: He likes to set himself up as an intellectual.
bilingual.target: 他喜欢自命为知识分子。
吕弗勒是我认识的一个花瓶一样的知识分子。

bilingual.source: How did the Indian modern intellectual form?

list.abstract: Intellectual，英语单词，形容词、名词，作形容词时意为“智力的；聪明的；理智的”，作名词时意为“知识分子；凭理智做事者”。

yingyinNormal.en: Our interest in this place is entirely in the intellectual property. The code.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们对这个地方唯一的兴趣就是知识产权，就是代码。

yingyinNormal.en: No, it was great. He just didn't really challenge me on an intellectual level.
yingyinNormal.zh: 不，其实还不错，只是他没有在智商层面上给我压力。

yingyinNormal.en: I just thought this time I'd go for something little more intellectual with a less painful final exam.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我决定换种课来上，换点比较要用脑袋，期末考又不用那么痛苦的。

yingyinNormal.en: Howard, please. This is Stephen Hawking. Perhaps my only intellectual equal. Oh, you can't be serious.
yingyinNormal.zh: 霍华德，求求你了，这可是史蒂芬·霍金啊，也许是唯一一个智商和我相当的人。你别搞笑了。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you them? We are members of the Abagail Adams Society of Intellectual Advancement. How may we be of service?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你们是吗？我们是阿比盖尔·亚当斯高智商社团的成员，有什么能为你们服务的？

yingyinNormal.en: Your hypothesis is completely disconfirmed by all the data. You're just clinging to it out of intellectual stubbornness.
yingyinNormal.zh: 种种数据显示，你的假设完全不能成立，现在纯粹是你的智商在死鸭子嘴硬。

yingyinNormal.en: Ladies, please. These four walls once housed an intellectual salon where the mind received nourishment as well as the stomach.
yingyinNormal.zh: 女士们，自制啊。这间屋子曾是一个智慧的集合地，在这里，大脑和胃袋都能吸收到营养。

yingyinNormal.en: I'm the child she was worried about? I have a brother and sister whose combined intellectual wattage couldn't power a potato clock, if I spotted them the potato.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她最担心的孩子居然是我？我有一个哥哥和一个姐姐，那两个人的智商瓦数加起来都不够给玩具土豆钟供电，而且还得是我帮他们指出土豆在哪。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, what do you know? Here I was, waiting to be bored with biology, and instead you tickle my intellectual fancy. Which, unlike my body, is an okay place to tickle.
yingyinNormal.zh: 真是没想到？本来我还等着要受无聊生物学的轰炸，结果却让你搔到了我求知的痒处。而这痒处不同于我的身体，是允许被搔的。

yingyinNormal.en: But, you're suggesting that I have emotional issues below my consciousness which drive my behavior, thus causing me to lash out at anything or anyone that threatens my intellectual superiority.
yingyinNormal.zh: 但是你是在暗示潜意识里我的情绪影响了我的行动，导致我大肆打击任何威胁到我智商优势的人或事吗？

yingyinNormal.en: What's your point? In order to keep hing a sexual relationship with Penny, I have to give up everything I believe in my intellectual integrity, the very nature of who I am? I can't do that, Howard.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你到底想说啥？为了和佩妮继续交往下去，我就得放弃我对科学知识的信仰和我的本性吗？我做不到，霍华德。

yingyinNormal.en: Now, if the Chinese are not willing to engage in a meaningful dialogue about intellectual property of American corporations, as well as this deliberate targeting of our government's online infrastructure.
yingyinNormal.zh: 如果中方没有诚意进行一场有意义的对话，探讨美国公司的知识产权，以及对我政府网络设施的蓄意攻击。

yingyinNormal.en: Can you see how a grown man, an accomplished scientist, who invests in a store that sells picture books about flying men in colorful underwear, might be wasting both his financial and intellectual resources?
yingyinNormal.zh: 你不觉得一个成年男子，而且是颇有成就的科学家，投资一家出售图画书主角是穿着色彩斑斓内裤的飞人们，也许是浪费他的财务和智力资源吗？
